
(MVI) Model View Intent

Model   - represents the state of UI. For example UI may have different states like loading, loaded, errors, 


View    - In MVI, view is interfaces which is implemented in Activity or Fragment.
        It means to have container which can accept the different model states and display it as a UI.

Event, Result, State, Effect

Event	- Any User's Event
Result	- Response from API, DB 
State	- Data Model Class
Effect	- UI Changes


